exercise.instructions:
1. After the HI_WORLD_ResetAppCmd() function protoype definition add the HI_WORLD_SetParamCmd() definition:
    bool HI_WORLD_SetParamCmd(void *ObjDataPtr, const CFE_MSG_Message_t *MsgPtr);
    Note this isn't required to compile the code, but is good practice if the function needs to be accessed by a unit test.

1. After the last CMDMGR_RegisterFunc() add
    CMDMGR_RegisterFunc(CMDMGR_OBJ, HI_WORLD_SET_PARAM_CC, NULL, HI_WORLD_SetParamCmd, sizeof(HI_WORLD_SetParam_CmdPayload_t));

Note HI_WORLD_SET_PARAM_CMD_CC is generated by the EDS toolchain
